  "title": "深度｜AI 吞噬软件，AI 构建 AI，来自达沃斯的 2026 预测",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247513640&idx=1&sn=ae9e8c6eb2fc1b6144cda2e190d38887",
  "date": "2026-01-25 11:01:00",
  "author": "Z Potentials",
  "siteName": "Z Potentials",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1365\" data-imgfileid=\"100029987\" data-ratio=\"0.66650390625\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2048\" data-width=\"2048\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=695f95ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZ300vPwLQkkiaRKoSKefqMTXjJvOVuVgD71nfTJXbVN87M4PExnMPUIDy8iceR7aL0fyz61vqj6BASCicaqMibRuUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">图片来源：</span></span></em><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">The World Economic Forum</span></span></em></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-size: 24px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">达沃斯的新隐喻</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2026年世界经济论坛，全球精英的目光聚焦到了一个新概念：Neural Spine，神经脊柱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这不仅是一个技术名词，更是一个精准的组织隐喻。企业正在寻找自己的智能核心，一个能感知、决策并协调的中枢系统。在瑞士达沃斯的雪山之巅，Lightspeed合伙人Ravi Mhatre、You.com创始人Richard Socher，以及来自中国的Kimi总裁张予彤围坐在一起。他们试图拆解一个核心命题：当AI不再是外挂的工具，而是成为组织的骨架时，企业会变成什么样。</span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-size: 24px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">定义“AI原生”的两种视角</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI时代，企业应如何设计组织、衡量效率？这不再是一个理论问题，而是一个迫在眉睫的实践挑战。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Ravi Mhatre，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Lightspeed合伙人</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">，也是Anthropic和Reflection AI的投资人，他</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">首先抛出了一个极具颠覆性的想象力框架，传统公司与AI原生公司的根本区别在于思维起点：“传统公司往往聚焦于现有技术和既定工作流，思考如何用AI优化存量；而真正的AI原生公司，思考的起点是‘</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">如果我们拥有无限的智能，我们应该创造什么？</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">’他们不受限于既有组织和流程的束缚。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这个“无限智能”的思维实验，引出了如何定义AI驱动型企业的话题。Rubric的创始人Bipul Sinha给出了一个可量化的业务视角：“当一家公司能在所有业务线中，有三到五个核心工作流是完全由AI实现的，它才能被真正视为AI驱动。”这意味着企业需要超越简单的信息搜索或ChatGPT界面调用，进入由AI自主执行完整业务流程的阶段。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在这一框架下，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Kimi</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">总裁张予彤提出了一个衡量未来组织效率的新颖度量单位：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">人与智能体比率（Human-to-Agent Ratio）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。她观察到，一些新兴公司，团队成员甚至不到10人，却拥有数百个智能体在运营层面协助处理大量事务。这背后，正是大模型驱动的组织设计（LLM-driven org design）所带来的惊人运营杠杆。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">变革并非一蹴而就。Richard Socher强调了技术之外人的因素。他认为多数人并非天生擅长管理AI智能体，有效的培训和认证体系，是帮助员工接纳并高效使用AI的关键。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">与此同时，一种自下而上的变革力量正在涌现。张予彤观察到“带上你自己的AI去上班”（BYOAI）的趋势。“我们通过用户调研发现，大量用户在工作中使用AI，并且愿意自掏腰包付费，”她分享道，“这表明个体生产力的觉醒，正与企业的顶层组织变革形成共振。”AI带来的不仅是效率，还有技能平权。一个生动的例子是：“我们现在收到的很多简历不再是PDF，而是个人网站链接。即使是完全不懂代码的求职者，也能通过AI生成精美的个人网站，充分展示自己的才华。”</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6030589949016751\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2746\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-width=\"2746\" data-height=\"1656\" data-imgfileid=\"100029988\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4cd2699&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZ300vPwLQkkiaRKoSKefqMTXjJvOVuVgDZxGmqicX8Fib2yH7NaPRtxCicAvx98L3aBYftht2IFwnfMDCEv6icQSRzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">图片来源：</span></span></em><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">The World Economic Forum</span></span></em></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-size: 24px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">软件正在“消失”？关于无形化的达沃斯共识</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">当讨论深入到工具层面，主持人引用了一个流行说法：「软件正在吞噬世界」曾是著名的预言，但现在大家说的是「AI正在吞噬软件」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">面对这个问题，张予彤给出了一个更精确的定义：软件不会消失，但它会变得无形。一场深刻的交互变革正在发生。过去的我们依赖点击、键盘，甚至记忆复杂的公式。未来，人类通过自然语言，就能经由智能体调用所有工具和软件的功能。如果现有软件无法满足需求，AI甚至可以利用其编码能力，即时生成个性化的工具来交付结果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Ravi Mhatre</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">认同</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">一</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">观点，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">并从投资视角给出了逻辑支撑。他指出，人们没有意识到AI能力的提升是一条陡峭的指数曲线。在过去一年，AI推理的平均单Token成本下降了100倍，在许多场景下甚至下降了1000倍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Ravi Mhatre补充，正是这条成本曲线，让智能本身变得极其廉价，从而催生了可丢弃软件（disposable software）的概念。代码可以被氛围化编写（vibe-coded），按需生成，也无需长期维护。不过他也提出了例外，对于像Instagram这样极其看重精细打磨的界面和用户内容生态的应用，传统的软件开发模式在长期内可能仍有其必要性。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5671875\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2560\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-width=\"2560\" data-height=\"1452\" data-imgfileid=\"100029986\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8373fe22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZ300vPwLQkkiaRKoSKefqMTXjJvOVuVgD180uSZfSyKH7RCotx2tRYzKYI1icUVtS6e6fI56RVFg8PgyxwQ6W8Pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">图片来源：</span></span></em><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">The World Economic Forum</span></span></em></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-size: 24px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">从试点到生产：跨越信任的鸿沟</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在AI成为企业“神经脊柱”之前，一个普遍的挑战必须被克服：信任。如何让企业放心地将核心业务交给一个“黑盒”？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Bipul Sinha指出了大型企业，尤其是美国公司面临的现实困境。合规与治理是AI落地最大的限制之一。许多客户从AI试点走向规模化生产的主要障碍，正是对合规风险的担忧。为此，Rubric的解法是构建一个合规基础设施，为不同业务职能预先定义允许使用的数据和经过认证的模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Richard Socher则从文化和方法论层面点出了另一个障碍。大多数传统公司缺乏基准测试或评估集的思维。他们需要建立一套更科学的流程来评估AI模型和智能体的表现，不能仅仅停留在感性的试用层面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">信任的建立，最终需要技术来支撑。You.com的创始人Richard Socher指出，他们的实践是通过提供清晰的引用来源，让每一个信息的出处都可追溯，这是他们最早申请专利并实现的功能之一。张予彤也认为，AI不能只提供一个直接答案，它必须通过展示思维链，将整个推理过程“开箱”给用户看。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这共同指明了AI从辅助工具走向企业核心的必经之路：透明度是信任的基石。只有当AI的思考过程变得可见、可追溯、可审查时，企业才能放心地将决策权交予它。</span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-size: 24px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">下一个常识是什么？2026年的AI趋势预测</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">当讨论走向尾声，主持人向嘉宾们提了一个未来式问题。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">今天听起来激进，但到明年此时会成为常识的事情是什么？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这个问题引发了一连串快速而精彩的预测：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Richard Socher的预测最为大胆：最好的AI将由AI自己来构建，而非人类。这意味着模型构建过程本身的自动化，以及递归式自我改进。他还预言，我们将看到模型具备持续学习能力的初步迹象，使其能动态适应环境变化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">张予彤则从应用层面构想，极长周期的自主代理将成为现实。她打了个比方，就像团队成员领走一个周度任务，一周后交付结果。未来的AI智能体也能独立处理跨度数周的复杂工作，并工作直至交付。谷歌DeepMind高管Ioannis Antonoglou也附议，他同样认为极长周期的自主代理会变得非常普遍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Bipul Sinha将目光投向了具体的AI技术应用。他认为，目前尚未被充分理解的强化学习，将在商业流程中得到广泛应用，并极大加速企业对AI的采纳。这意味着AI将能动态优化营销活动、供应链管理等复杂系统，不再只是执行预设指令。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Bipul Sinha还强调了智能体编排的重要性，未来将出现一个“编排者”，能够根据需求动态创建和组合各种工作流。而Ioannis Antonoglou则指出了更深层的挑战，即多智能体系统的动力学问题。当多个AI智能体与人类在同一个系统中交互时，其行为和涌现现象目前尚无坚实的科学基础去理解和优化，这将是一个紧迫的研究课题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">效率的追求，也折射出不同区域的发展路径。讨论中，主持人曾向张予彤提问，并提到“让你代表整个中国可能不公平”，但这恰恰引出了关于中国AI生态独特性的探讨。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">从创业第一天起就明确，在无法比拼算力规模的不对称竞争中，必须通过极致的基础研究创新换取效率。这种效率追求，与中国在市场规模、用户开放心态和基建先行带来的低成本能源优势相结合，共同构成了其独特的竞争力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这场对话并未给出所有答案，但它清晰地指明了方向：未来的商业竞争，将是关于“神经脊柱”的竞争，是关于“人与智能体比率”的竞争，更是关于构建信任与拥抱变革的想象力的竞争。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;\"><em><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">资料来源：</span></span></strong></em></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;\"><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://cn.weforum.org/meetings/world-economic-forum-annual-meeting-2026/sessions/enterprises-with-a-neural-spine/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.weforum.org/meetings/world-economic-forum-annual-meeting-2026/sessions/enterprises-with-a-neural-spine/?utm_source=chatgpt.com</a></span></span></em></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇集了 2026 达沃斯论坛上关于 AI 原生组织、软件无形化及自主智能体的深度预测，探讨了 AI 如何从工具演变为企业的“神经脊柱”。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇集了 2026 达沃斯论坛上关于 AI 原生组织、软件无形化及自主智能体的深度预测，探讨了 AI 如何从工具演变为企业的“神经脊柱”。",
  "summary": "文章记录了 2026 年达沃斯论坛上，来自 Lightspeed、You.com 及 Kimi 的行业领袖对 AI 未来的共识。核心观点包括：企业正向“神经脊柱”架构演进，衡量效率的新标准将是“人与智能体比率”；软件将通过自然语言交互变得“无形”，甚至出现按需生成、无需维护的“可丢弃软件”；AI 落地生产环境的关键在于通过透明的思维链和合规基础设施构建信任。最后，专家预测未来 AI 将自主构建 AI，且长周期自主代理将成为商业常态。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "提出“人与智能体比率”作为衡量 AI 驱动型组织效率的新度量单位。",
      "explanation": "未来组织将由少数人类和大量智能体构成，通过大模型驱动的组织设计获得极高的运营杠杆，实现技能平权和个体生产力觉醒。"
    },
    {
      "point": "软件正在变得“无形”，并催生出“可丢弃软件”的概念。",
      "explanation": "随着 AI 推理成本大幅下降，代码可以按需生成（Vibe-coded）并即时交付结果，传统软件的点击交互将被自然语言和智能体调用取代。"
    },
    {
      "point": "透明度是 AI 从试点走向规模化生产并跨越信任鸿沟的基石。",
      "explanation": "企业需要通过展示 AI 的思维链（CoT）和构建合规基础设施，使 AI 的决策过程可追溯、可审查，从而解决黑盒带来的治理风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "预测未来最好的 AI 将由 AI 自己构建，并实现递归式自我改进。",
      "explanation": "模型构建过程将实现自动化，且具备持续学习能力，能够独立处理跨度数周的复杂任务并最终交付结果。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "真正的 AI 原生公司，思考的起点是‘如果我们拥有无限的智能，我们应该创造什么？’",
    "软件不会消失，但它会变得无形。人类通过自然语言，就能经由智能体调用所有工具和软件的功能。",
    "代码可以被氛围化编写（vibe-coded），按需生成，也无需长期维护。",
    "最好的 AI 将由 AI 自己来构建，而非人类。这意味着模型构建过程本身的自动化，以及递归式自我改进。",
    "未来的商业竞争，将是关于‘神经脊柱’的竞争，是关于‘人与智能体比率’的竞争。"
  ],
  "tags": [
